    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project or budget-friendly daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. Mechanically, it starts and runs, though it shows its age with some minor fluid seeps and a suspension that is beginning to feel soft. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading on the clear coat, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and carpet. All major electronics are currently functional, but the AC takes a while to get cold. It is a reliable runner for now, but expect to address some maintenance items in the near future.",
      "price": 22500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
